text.tspan: Estimated and projected life expectancy at birth, United Kingdom, 1981 to 2091
Estimated (historic) and projected life expectancy, measured as the average expected years at birth. This is given for
the ONS's 2014 and 2016 revision of life expectancy projections.
Data source: UK Office for National Statistics (ONS)
